## Available Commands

### Plan Management

#### Create Plan
```bash
aur plan create "{{ goal }}"
```

Creates the eight-file plan structure in `.aurora/plans/active/{{ plan_id }}/`

#### View Plan
```bash
aur plan view {{ plan_id }}
```

Displays plan dashboard with progress, subgoals, and status.

#### List Plans
```bash
aur plan list
aur plan list --archived
aur plan list --all
```

Lists active, archived, or all plans.

#### Archive Plan
```bash
aur plan archive {{ plan_id }}
aur plan archive {{ plan_id }} --force
```

Archives completed plan to `.aurora/plans/archive/YYYY-MM-DD-{{ plan_id }}/`

